  "keyFeatures": [
    "Pre-trained 3B parameter vision-language-action foundation model",
    "Cross-embodiment generalization across humanoid and manipulation robots",
    "Fine-tuning on custom robot datasets with minimal data",
    "Support for multiple robot embodiments (GR1, G1, Panda, WidowX, etc.)",
    "Server-client architecture for remote inference",
    "Open-loop and closed-loop evaluation frameworks",
    "Integration with simulation benchmarks (LIBERO, SimplerEnv, BEHAVIOR)",
    "LeRobot v2 compatible data format"
